                                                                                style="margin: 0 0 25px 0; color: #c0c0c0;">
                                                                                Thank you once again for choosing to be
                                                                                a part of the <strong
                                                                                    style="color: #ff6b6b;">
                                                                                    <%= data.eventName %>
                                                                                </strong>. We wish you the best of luck,
                                                                                and we can't wait to see you showcase
                                                                                your talents!
                                                                            </p>

                                                                            <!-- Signature -->
                                                                            <table border="0" cellpadding="15"
                                                                                cellspacing="0" width="100%"
                                                                                style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0000 0%, #0d0000 100%); background-color: #1a0000; border: 1px solid #8b0000; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 30px;">
